<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/ui-system.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/legal.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="legal-shell mx-auto">
            <div class="legal-surface">
                <div class="legal-header">
                    <span class="legal-kicker">Legal Information</span>
                    <h1 class="legal-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
                </div>

                <div class="legal-body">
                    <div class="legal-note mb-4">
                        These notes describe the current data processing and cookie usage in this application.
                        The currently published version is authoritative.
                    </div>

                    <h2 class="h5">General Information</h2>
                    <p>
                        This application processes personal data only as required to provide the service,
                        user accounts, and uploaded training data.
                    </p>

                    <h2 class="h5">Processed Data</h2>
                    <p>
                        Depending on usage, this may include contact details, account details, login information,
                        and uploaded FIT/training data.
                    </p>

                    <h2 class="h5">Purpose of Processing</h2>
                    <p>
                        Data processing is used for authentication, application delivery, training analysis,
                        and technical protection of operations.
                    </p>

                    <h2 class="h5">Cookies and Similar Technologies</h2>
                    <p>
                        This application currently uses only technically necessary cookies for login,
                        session management, and security. Optional analytics or marketing cookies
                        are not currently used.
                    </p>

                    <h2 class="h5">Technically Necessary Cookies in Use</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li><code>connect.sid</code> (session management)</li>
                        <li><code>accessToken</code> (authentication for protected areas)</li>
                        <li><code>refreshToken</code> (login renewal)</li>
                        <li><code>idToken</code> (identity information inside the application)</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>
                        These cookies are required for core functionality and are not used for advertising
                        or tracking purposes.
                    </p>

                    <h2 class="h5">Legal Basis</h2>
                    <p>
                        Where cookies or similar technologies are strictly required to provide the application,
                        their use is based on § 25 para. 2 no. 2 TDDDG. Subsequent personal data processing is based,
                        depending on context, on Art. 6 para. 1 lit. b GDPR (contract performance) and
                        Art. 6 para. 1 lit. f GDPR (legitimate interest in secure and stable operations).
                    </p>

                    <h2 class="h5">Privacy Contact</h2>
                    <p>
                        The responsible entity and contact options are listed in the <a href="/impressum">Legal Notice</a>.<br>
                        If you use a dedicated privacy contact, add it here as well.
                    </p>

                    <div class="mt-4">
                        <a class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm" href="<%= returnTo %>">Back to application</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
